{
  "stem": "19939.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No And no, and even the first action, we were in the house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we heard shooting, and we heard these mens were shot, and this one was shot, and whatever was taken.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But somehow I never witnessed this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I was in the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now next, people started to have to save themselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some people-- so I had this-- you know, we were going out with my stepmother, from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it wasn't closed yet, which were the boundaries.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were going to my boss, who was an important figure in this Debica, In that township or something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was willing to help out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, we were bringing him things from the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had some beautiful-- whatever, linens or--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Silk, I remember this was handmade, whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And women started-- you know, started also this-- the Poles were being sent to work in Germany, like conscription, right.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every something from the village had to give so many people to work to Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the people started somehow procured some false papers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know some people were running away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was not too much communication.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, our neighbors were gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a-- at the time there were neighbors that had a bakery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a-- a guy that had his legs amputated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His best friend had to take him out to be shot, and he was pleading with them to shot him in the head, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they just did the opposite.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened to me, I had no papers, right?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I've heard that one of the girls went to this gathering, whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was recognized that she was Jewish by the Polish people that she was sent back.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
